query:
SELECT s.id, s.status, s.completedHotels, s.totalHotels, COUNT(sr.id) as result_count 
FROM scans s 
LEFT JOIN scanResults sr ON s.id = sr.scanId 
WHERE s.id >= 30000 
GROUP BY s.id 
ORDER BY s.id DESC 
LIMIT 5
